  "texts": [
    "We generated GPT reappraisals using OpenAI's GPT-4-0314 model.",
    "We accessed the API via the \"chat completion\" endpoint.",
    "Each API request consists of a userdefined \"system message\" and \"messages [history]\", which together form the \"request body\".",
    "The system message customizes the model's response, and the message history, a collection of previous interactions between the user and the model, provides context to further guide the model's answers.",
    "Since our goal was to explore GPT's reappraisal ability at its default settings, we did not adjust the system message and left it as \"You are a helpful assistant.\""
  ],
